data.description: **UPDATE OFFER DEADLINE 11/20 BY 4:00PM.**Start your next chapter here! The feeling of warmth & home greets you upon entering this well maintained 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath Fully Dormer Cape w/ farmer's porch. The spacious eat in kitchen includes granite counter tops, SS appliances, center island. Set behind the kitchen is a sun drenched 4 season room with cathedral ceilings & access to the private deck & yard. The casualness of the FP'd living room invites you in as you arrive making it a great place to unwind. The formal dining room completes the main level. As you make your way up the stairs the large bright front to back primary bedroom offers a sense of relaxation after a long day. You will arrive at two more bedrooms & full bathroom. The super dry lower level features an extra large family room/man cave/gym. You decide! The possibilities are endless! Other features: 2 car attached tandem heated garage, central air, central vac, fenced in yard, storage shed.
